column4: Where is the ubuntu (distributor-logo) icon logo located that is on the panel next to "applications"?  I'm using a custom theme and not sure which folder the logo is in as a slocate turns up up like 9 results
I think the logo is in /usr/share/icons/hicolor/distributor-logo.png or something
ok thanks, just wasn't sure of the right one
It was that in Breezy I think, but I've lost all of my custom icons I made so I haven't bothered changing it in Dapper yet
